<!doctype lake><title>利益演示</title><meta name="doc-version" content="1" /><meta name="viewport" content="fixed" /><meta name="typography" content="classic" /><meta name="paragraphSpacing" content="relax" /><h2 data-lake-id="KPQdC" id="KPQdC" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u330a1783" id="u330a1783">增额终生寿</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="fPER4" id="fPER4" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u72a0f71c" id="u72a0f71c">现金价值计算方式：</span></h3><ol list="u430427ef"><li fid="ua623965b" data-lake-id="u82832f6f" id="u82832f6f"><span data-lake-id="u92f03377" id="u92f03377" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">基本保额=查表</span><span data-lake-id="u3ddda90c" id="u3ddda90c" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #DF2A3F">1000元</span><span style="color: #DF2A3F"><u><span data-lake-id="ua51150da" id="ua51150da" class="lake-fontsize-12">保费</span></u></span><span data-lake-id="u9e2cf2b4" id="u9e2cf2b4" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">对应基本保额*首期保费对1000的倍数</span><span data-lake-id="u2d79a3ce" id="u2d79a3ce" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">➗</span><span data-lake-id="ua25e89ac" id="ua25e89ac" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">交费方式的系数</span></li><li fid="ua623965b" data-lake-id="u44d628c6" id="u44d628c6"><span data-lake-id="uc2c18ba8" id="uc2c18ba8" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">首期保费对1000的倍数=首期保费</span><span data-lake-id="u66db2efb" id="u66db2efb" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">➗</span><span data-lake-id="ua11a7803" id="ua11a7803" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">1000</span></li><li fid="ua623965b" data-lake-id="uaa72138a" id="uaa72138a"><span data-lake-id="ue07f622e" id="ue07f622e" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">现金价值（保证）=基本保额对1000的倍数*</span><span data-lake-id="u0559a356" id="u0559a356" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #DF2A3F">1000</span><span style="color: #DF2A3F"><u><span data-lake-id="uda0f7316" id="uda0f7316" class="lake-fontsize-12">基本保险金额</span></u></span><span data-lake-id="uf71f61d1" id="uf71f61d1" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">对应的现金价值=（索引出的1000基本保额</span><span data-lake-id="u6fafa251" id="u6fafa251" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">➗</span><span data-lake-id="uf5737bd2" id="uf5737bd2" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">1000）*（索引出的1000元现金价值）</span></li><li fid="ua623965b" data-lake-id="u1e423bea" id="u1e423bea"><span data-lake-id="u20c7975e" id="u20c7975e" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">基本保额对1000的倍数=基本保额</span><span data-lake-id="ua3bc6135" id="ua3bc6135" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">➗</span><span data-lake-id="ueab706f1" id="ueab706f1" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">1000</span></li><li fid="ua623965b" data-lake-id="u7ef65112" id="u7ef65112"><span data-lake-id="u6900b29d" id="u6900b29d" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">现金价值（保证+分红）=现金价值（保证）+累积分红对应的保额对应的现金价值=现金价值（保证）+（根据∑截止当前保单年度查表历年分红保额</span><span data-lake-id="u308e40a8" id="u308e40a8" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">➗</span><span data-lake-id="u5a4eb5d8" id="u5a4eb5d8" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">1000）*索引出1000现金价值</span></li></ol><h3 data-lake-id="Ba77w" id="Ba77w" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ue5fdea23" id="ue5fdea23">所需附表数据</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id="N4mjw" id="N4mjw" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u4f2bdf3a" id="u4f2bdf3a" style="color: #000000">表1-基本保额表（1000元）。按如下笛卡尔积形式展开提供</span></h4><table data-lake-id="rzXig" id="rzXig" row-head="#074A92;#D9EAFC" class="lake-table" style="width: 655px"><colgroup><col width="222"><col width="116"><col width="130"><col width="187"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u21d96bbb" id="u21d96bbb" style="height: 38px"><td data-lake-id="u33e9b2b4" id="u33e9b2b4"><p data-lake-id="ud9d0cb37" id="ud9d0cb37"><span data-lake-id="u5a4f8ea1" id="u5a4f8ea1" class="lake-fontsize-12" style="color: #000000">交费期间</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u436